{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/xiang-yu-ni-tian-huang-di-lao-zhi-dao-fang-zi-pa-man-hua-cao/","webpackCompilationHash":"6aeeaaa382e6a1351e99","result":{"data":{"ghostPost":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d11c27c95f47f3656854118","title":"想与你天荒地老，直到房子爬满花草。","slug":"xiang-yu-ni-tian-huang-di-lao-zhi-dao-fang-zi-pa-man-hua-cao","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/2_meitu_2-10.jpg","excerpt":"陪伴是最长情的告白，我愿在老去之年，仍然能够安静的陪在你身边","custom_excerpt":"陪伴是最长情的告白，我愿在老去之年，仍然能够安静的陪在你身边","created_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","published_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"27 June, 2019","created_at":"2019-06-25T14:43:08.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-06-25T14:46:17.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-06-27T15:21:19.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"}],"primary_author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"},"primary_tag":{"name":"建筑绿化","slug":"jianzhu-lu-hua","description":"建筑绿化、垂直绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"建筑绿化","slug":"jianzhu-lu-hua","description":"建筑绿化、垂直绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"}],"plaintext":"陪伴是最长情的告白，\n\n我愿在老去之年，\n\n仍然能够安静的陪在你身边~\n\n在院子里，\n\n种上一些爬山虎，\n\n经年累月，\n\n让它陪我们一起共赴终老的岁月。\n\n如果你喜欢紫藤萝，\n\n随便也可以栽一两株在窗前，\n\n让它随着清风摇曳~\n\n春天，\n\n我们的家是充满希望的绿意；\n\n到了秋天，\n\n秋色也会悄然爬上我们的小房，\n\n秋意浓浓~\n\n石板路，小栅栏，\n\n我们的房子会随着岁月流逝越加古朴美丽，\n\n就如我们相爱相依的感情。\n\n我会偷偷种一株玫瑰在你窗前，\n\n当你开窗时，\n\n会不经意发现它在为你盛放。\n\n或许我们门前，\n\n会有一条清澈见底的溪流，\n\n它欢快的流向远方，\n\n让我们感受上善若水，心情也愈加平静~\n\n闲暇的午后，\n\n与你相伴坐在玫瑰花架下，\n\n笑着读你当年为我写下的那些肉麻的情话~\n\n日子就这样一天天过着，\n\n花团锦簇下是我们美好的年华。\n\n就想这样与你天荒地老，\n\n直到我们的房子长满花花草草~","html":"<p>陪伴是最长情的告白，</p><p>我愿在老去之年，</p><p>仍然能够安静的陪在你身边~</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/1_meitu_1-10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>在院子里，</p><p>种上一些爬山虎，</p><p>经年累月，</p><p>让它陪我们一起共赴终老的岁月。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/2_meitu_2-9.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/3_meitu_3-9.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>如果你喜欢紫藤萝，</p><p>随便也可以栽一两株在窗前，</p><p>让它随着清风摇曳~</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/4_meitu_4-11.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/5_meitu_5-10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>春天，</p><p>我们的家是充满希望的绿意；</p><p>到了秋天，</p><p>秋色也会悄然爬上我们的小房，</p><p>秋意浓浓~</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/6_meitu_6-10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/7_meitu_7-4.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>石板路，小栅栏，</p><p>我们的房子会随着岁月流逝越加古朴美丽，</p><p>就如我们相爱相依的感情。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/8_meitu_8-5.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/9_meitu_9-4.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>我会偷偷种一株玫瑰在你窗前，</p><p>当你开窗时，</p><p>会不经意发现它在为你盛放。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/10_meitu_10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/11_meitu_11-5.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>或许我们门前，</p><p>会有一条清澈见底的溪流，</p><p>它欢快的流向远方，</p><p>让我们感受上善若水，心情也愈加平静~</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/12_meitu_12-2.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/13_meitu_13-2.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>闲暇的午后，</p><p>与你相伴坐在玫瑰花架下，</p><p>笑着读你当年为我写下的那些肉麻的情话~</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/15_meitu_16.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>日子就这样一天天过着，</p><p>花团锦簇下是我们美好的年华。</p><p>就想这样与你天荒地老，</p><p>直到我们的房子长满花花草草~</p>","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/xiang-yu-ni-tian-huang-di-lao-zhi-dao-fang-zi-pa-man-hua-cao/","uuid":"3b871e76-d595-4947-bd9f-4120e55137de","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d11c27c95f47f3656854118"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"xiang-yu-ni-tian-huang-di-lao-zhi-dao-fang-zi-pa-man-hua-cao"}}}